Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ran, you really are unrivaled!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having won the Kanto Karate Championship and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all thanks to the "Rounding Heel\NKick" Kazumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for her opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, today I'll treat you to the cake buffet at\NHaido Hotel as promised, so eat and get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to eat a lot and get super, super strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't you get fat instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If all cases were men...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose the invisible mysteries would be women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet another rival for Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A handsome detective's mysterious appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,DEDUCTION SHOWDOWN AT THE HAUNTED HOTEL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you told him about your victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also gave him your answer to that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hel-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The answer to that guy's confession in London!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did inform him about my victory, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not my reply to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I also only reported my victory through email...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I just feel uneasy talking to him directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"WHAT THE FLIPPING HECK, LADY"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize how many days it's been since then!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, how many days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is now like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Ran, why hasn't she responded to my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me she has someone else in her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, if that's the case, I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice but to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Cry until these tears are used up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably depressed with those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you think I'm like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take it too slow, Shimchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} may have a change of heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His attitude is kind of uh-uh, but he's surprisingly popular, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Uh-uh"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, a powerful rival may suddenly appear, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy's a groper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't act all innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You touched my butt just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, it's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm done for if I get hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Kanto's champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeet Kune Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pervert is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would let me explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person's not a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw how that person seized the hand\Nresponsible for touching Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then that's how Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} mistook that person's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,WAS YOU!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never show yourself again, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I almost kicked you without even making sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad we've cleared up our misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On second look, what a hot guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're my type...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pervert's victim was me, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Haido Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm headed to that hotel too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better not be making that up, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have no vacancies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come, I made a reservation, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sincere apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should have declined, but our oversight caused the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it sure seems he really has some business with the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, any other rooms available?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are currently renovating our hotel annex, so we\Nhave fewer rooms available and are now all occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, let's hurry and go eat some cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, isn't he so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as strong as you, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he fought with Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I wonder\Nwhose karate would be stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Jeet Kune Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeet Kune Do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Movie star Bruce Lee took the art of Kung\NFu he had been practicing as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:07:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And combined it with boxing, judo, wrestling, savate, aikido\Nand other forms of fighting to develop this martial art!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it has a number of attacks that target vital points\Nsuch as the eyes and throat, so it's pretty fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, you know all kinds of weird things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, where are they having the cake buffet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've come to a place where there's somehow nobody around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the net, it says it's at the cafe on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go to the second floor and take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are elevators over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, where are you going, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the cake buffet on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you can't get there using this elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one goes to the annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't they say the annex was under renovation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should help each other when in need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hirukawa Toshiko (49)\NHousewife
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first he was drunk and shouting curses as usual, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I scolded him severely, he started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He cried?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that, after he had sobered up, he'd apologize to\Neveryone and admit his sins, so he'd like us to go to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he just be planning to spew nonsense to dodge our question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to get us off his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might say that he doesn't remember saying\Nanything of the sort if we ask him about it later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we record his repentance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, the other victims could hear it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't have any recording devices with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's take my car and the three of us can buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he said it'd be a while before he sobered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we should be able to find at least\None electronics shop in this area, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're cutting off the line for the cake buffet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More customers than we'd expected\Ncame, so there weren't enough cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cake Buffet\NAll-you-can-eat and unlimited soft drinks for 90 mins\N[ NOW CLOSED ]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to hold a cake buffet, you should\Nprepare a whole lot and go out with a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}bang{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just backing up the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When this man fell from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Uesumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, who's that over there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone suspicious was on the roof just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what that person looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw the clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might have been an acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, call the police and keep watch\Nover this place with the security guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going with these people to the roof to take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this elevator has both front and rear doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Hirukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't I just stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who saw them, Hirukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoes on top of a jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suicide!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what was the person's shadow that Hirukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind making this jacket flutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pushed him too hard with my words
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this was most likely
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you saw someone push him off from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to overhear your conversation stating\Nthat the man who fell to his death was quite drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to my line of work, my ears are quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your line of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why isn't this a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, his shoes are even lined up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just a preconception, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen innumerable jumper suicide scenes up until now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just about none of the bodies had been shoeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've seen innumerable jumper suicide scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess the most influential theory would be\Nthat it's a key plot device in movies or TV dramas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you see shoes lined up on a roof, there's a suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be a convenience condition for\Ndramas to strike that chord emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nowadays not so much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same goes for detective dramas in the past that would show\Nblood gushing out of the mouths of people who hung themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In reality, blood will not flow out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's easier for viewers to understand\Nthe death, and it packed more impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having seen those sorts of dramas or movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are cases of those who'd think they ought\Nto remove their shoes before jumping off, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:13:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing as how the man who fell to his death had been\Nheavily intoxicated and requested time to sober up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a groggy state...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd do things such as take his\Njacket off and place his shoes neatly atop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even the possibility that some random\Nperson placed this here as a prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be rejected since the shoes are directly\Nabove where the man fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that brings us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No other conclusion than, to disguise it as a jumper suicide\Nthe culprit deliberately lined the shoes up here, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the culprit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet they'll be arrested real soon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since, before I came up here to the roof, I asked the\Nguard to keep watch over the elevator and stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Sera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this little boy here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there wasn't anyone at all\Nexcept this fallen man in the annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the guard who had been\Nwatching elevators and stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all were the only ones who had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, just who would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another one of these pain-in-the-necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why was this man there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The annex was under renovation, so nobody should've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased Uesumi Teigo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the\Nson of the owner of this Haido Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They made an exception and let him use one of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to avoid the media, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By "media"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that person famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was arrested in the past for being\Nthe ringleader of a remittance scam...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But was acquitted on insufficient proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And is now creating trouble for the weeklies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the media caught wind of it, and a huge\Nuproar about it went on until last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} flew off the handle at his media interviewers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And broke the sixth floor window with a fire extinguisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, guests stopped staying in the annex\Nand even the hotel couldn't abide him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There had been rumors that they were using the annex\Nrenovation as an excuse to force him to move overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we victims also heard that rumor\Nand that's why we came to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he could flee overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wanted him to at least give an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, were you able to meet Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the first one to go to his room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly burst into tears and said that\Nhe'd admit to his crimes and apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But said he wanted some time to sober up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we might as well record his repentance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the three of us decided to go and buy a\Nrecording device from a nearby electronics shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got into my car in the parking lot, but just as we backed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He dropped down right before our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you backed up the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be that someone pulled a string or something\Nthat tied Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to the car and made him fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anyone who touched your car or the body after he fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as this lady said she saw a suspicious figure on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I immediately went up to the roof with her and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the meantime, I told Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s group\Nto help the guard and watch the car and the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the suspicious figure was something I mistook, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, there may still be traces of some sort of contraption.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspect it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I was waiting for the elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it stopped on the sixth and second floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When there had been a commotion about a fallen man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after this little boy brought the lady and the\Nothers to the elevator and headed to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The elevator went nonstop to the top floor\Nbut took its time coming back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if I recall, there should have been two elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears that only one had been working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they figured Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the only one staying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it may be that someone else is still lurking in the annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scene investigators are searching every nook and cranny, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No reports of anyone having been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The surveillance cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're in the elevator and the hallways, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About those...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wreaked havoc, he\Nsprayed paint all over the hotel annex...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even the surveillance cameras were all sprayed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all blacked out and nothing can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, the inside of the annex is a blackbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one can tell for sure who did what inside of it, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This just got exciting, right, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please watch what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person just passed away, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it's necessary for us to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second and sixth floors where, for some\Nreason, the elevator supposedly stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That had to have been the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if you tell that to the police detectives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just tell them anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a rumor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said it will come out in this annex...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ghost, it's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:19:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At night, people have seen an unoccupied wheelchair that\Nbelonged to an elderly man roaming around the annex!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be that ghost was the one who pushed the elevator button...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If no one was sitting in the wheelchair...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you know it was an elderly man's ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who fell victim to the remittance scam was my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she collapsed due to the shock and had to be hospitalized, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father deliberately booked a room in the annex so that\Nhe could beg in front of Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying, "I won't ask you to return the\Nmoney, but please apologize to my wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when my father found out about my mother's\Ndeath in the hospital, on the evening of that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He committed suicide in the room he was staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father had been using an electric wheelchair\Non loan from the hotel due to his disabilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's how the rumor started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, what room did your father stay in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This graffiti certainly is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice but to renovate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is there a wheelchair here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I found it, it was still moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there was weird fishing line attached\Nbetween the wheels, I checked with the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said this was the electric wheelchair that\Nthe fallen Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been borrowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did he have bad legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it seems he was just using it to cruise around the annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an unbelievable guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the one\Nbehind the aforementioned ghost commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had planned to scare the three victims who came to\Nvisit on 2F where the elderly man committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By manipulating the unoccupied wheelchair\Nwith a fishing line - if we think of it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would certainly make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, this fishing line is extremely long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are some broken rubber bands at the tip of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The footrests have marks indicating they've bumped into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man who fell to his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the ringleader of a remittance fraud group that\Nhad caused a public uproar â€”\hUesumi Teigo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and other victims from\Nhis scam visited this Haido Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While waiting for Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who had weeped\Nand admitted to his crimes, to sober up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They decided to go buy a recording device for his\Nconfession, and just as they started driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came tumbling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the roof, we found Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nclothes and shoes lined up perfectly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was actually a setup to disguise this as a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the testimony of this self-proclaimed detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After we had rushed up to the roof, he saw the elevator\Nstopping at 6F and 2F before coming down to 1F.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a wheelchair still in motion was found on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A long line had been tied between the wheels\Nwith broken rubber bands attached at the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this mean that the culprit utilized this\Nwheelchair to make Uesumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fall to his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how did they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, just who is this guy calling himself "Sera"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will Sera's careless deduction send\Nthe whole case down a blind alley?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My last resort is to use Shmichi's voice to solve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paint Cans
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.14,0:24:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's such a handsome chum!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.40,0:24:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll find out next week!
